  • Packages that use sx.blah.discord.handle.audio 
    Package Description
    sx.blah.discord.handle.audio
    This package contains all audio-related components.

    This package contains the default implementations of interfaces from the sx.blah.discord.handle.audio package.
    sx.blah.discord.handle.impl.obj
    This package contains all the implemented versions of Discord objects.
    sx.blah.discord.handle.obj
    This contains the interfaces Discord4J users directly interact with.

    This package contains events which are dispatched by AudioPlayer.
    sx.blah.discord.util.audio.processors
    This contains implementations of IAudioProcessor.
    sx.blah.discord.util.audio.providers
    This contains implementations of IAudioProvider.
